Please list the versions of VE, EMF and GEF you installed that caused this problem.

The VE 1.0 M1 build does not run under RC1.  Download the latest Integration
build instead.

This are the versions:

emf-runtime-I200403250631.zip
GEF-runtime-I20040330.zip
VE-runtime-1.0M1.zip

That's the problem then, you were attempting to run VE 1.0 M1 on Eclipse 3.0
RC1.  VE 1.0 M1 required Eclipse 3.0 M8.  Please try the latest Integration
build of VE, and it's required versions of GEF and EMF.  These should run on
Eclipse 3.0 RC1 correctly.

As Jeff indicated you must be on the latest VE integration build (20040611) to
work with RC1.
Since this bug was not reOpened for more than a month, this bug is verified.
